name: DateJar
0:
”Alexa, ask date jar to find a free date”
”Alexa, ask date jar to find me a date”
”Alexa, open date jar”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: date jar
des: Having trouble coming up with an activity for date night? Ask Date Jar to pick an idea for you, you can select from dates based on location, cost, or categories like romantic, adventurous or at home dates. Or you can just ask Alexa to pick a date at random. Enable location permissions for the skill in the Alexa app for a fuller experience with date suggestions based on your zip code.
